e skill offers different operations/capabilities\n-23 - Example: PDF skill with \"Quick Start\" -> \"Merge PDFs\" -> \"Split PDFs\" -> \"Extract Text\"\n-24 - Structure: ## Overview -> ## Quick Start -> ## Task Category 1 -> ## Task Category 2...\n+26 ## 详细工作流程\n 25 \n-26 **3. Reference/Guidelines** (best for standards or specifications)\n-27 - Works well for brand guidelines, coding standards, or requirements\n-28 - Example: Brand styling with \"Brand Guidelines\" -> \"Colors\" -> \"Typography\" -> \"Features\"\n-29 - Structure: ## Overview -> ## Guidelines -> ## Specifications -> ## Usage...\n-30 \n-31 **4. Capabilities-Based** (best for integrated systems)\n-32 - Works well when the skill provides multiple interrelated features\n-33 - Example: Product Management with \"Core Capabilities\" -> numbered capability list\n-34 - Structure: ## Overview -> ## Core Capabilities -> ### 1. Feature -> ### 2. Feature...\n-35 \n-36 Patterns can be mixed and matched as needed. Most skills combine patterns (e.g., start with task-based, add workflow for complex operations).\n-37 \n-38 Delete this entire \"Structuring This Skill\" section when done - it's just guidance.]\n-39 \n 40 ## [TODO: Replace with the first main section based on chosen structure]\n 41 \n 42 [TODO: Add content here. See examples in existing skills:\n 43 - Code samples for technical skills\n    ...","firstChangedLine":3},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776130214924}}
{"type":"message","id":"fef9317a","parentId":"76aa12f2","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:30:20.682Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在添加详细步骤。继续编辑。我需要包含每个步骤的具体操作、使用的工具和注意事项。先读取当前文件看看。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_7rJHEoGjbIvAQ5pE9oQM3Vsf","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/SKILL.md","offset":30,"limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":1052,"output":147,"cacheRead":24832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776130214926,"responseId":"09fd863d-6c0b-43c8-bc41-98618db32e01"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e81f4ff","parentId":"fef9317a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:30:20.688Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_7rJHEoGjbIvAQ5pE9oQM3Vsf","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[TODO: Add content here. See examples in existing skills:\n- Code samples for technical skills\n- Decision trees for complex workflows\n- Concrete examples with realistic user requests\n- References to scripts/templates/references as needed]\n\n## Resources (optional)\n\nCreate only the resource directories this skill actually needs. Delete this section if no resources are required.\n\n### scripts/\nExecutable code (Python/Bash/etc.) that can be run directly to perform specific operations.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- PDF skill: `fill_fillable_fields.py`, `extract_form_field_info.py` - utilities for PDF manipulation\n- DOCX skill: `document.py`, `utilities.py` - Python modules for document processing\n\n**Appropriate for:** Python scripts, shell scripts, or any executable code that performs automation, data processing, or specific operations.\n\n**Note:** Scripts may be executed without loading into context, but can still be read by Codex for patching or environment adjustments.\n\n### references/\nDocumentation and reference material intended to be loaded into context to inform Codex's process and thinking.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- Product management: `communication.md`, `context_building.md` - detailed workflow guides\n- BigQuery: API reference documentation and query examples\n- Finance: Schema documentation, company policies\n\n**Appropriate for:** In-depth documentation, API references, database schemas, comprehensive guides, or any detailed information that Codex should reference while working.\n\n### assets/\nFiles not intended to be loaded into context, but rather used within the output Codex produces.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- Brand styling: PowerPoint template files (.pptx), logo files\n- Frontend builder: HTML/React boilerplate project directories\n- Typography: Font files (.ttf, .woff2)\n\n**Appropriate for:** Templates, boilerplate code, document templates, images, icons, fonts, or any files meant to be copied or used in the final output.\n\n---\n\n**Not every skill requires all three types of resources.**\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776130220687}}
{"type":"message","id":"6bd06404","parentId":"2e81f4ff","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:31:19.795Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要替换掉“TODO: Add content here”部分，添加详细步骤。先删除这部分并插入详细工作流。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_9LjkQ11piX62UDFHxoZhjRNc","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"[TODO: Add content here. See examples in existing skills:\n- Code samples for technical skills\n- Decision trees for complex workflows\n- Concrete examples with realistic user requests\n- References to scripts/templates/references as needed]","newText":"### 步骤1：公司选择与审核\n\n**目标**：从AI科技公司名单中选择一家尚未分析或超过1年未分析的公司。\n\n**操作流程**：\n1. 检查 `memory/companies.json` 文件（如果不存在则创建初始名单）\n2. 初始名单条件：至少完成A轮融资的AI科技公司\n3. 每日检查是否有新公司可加入（通过web_search搜索最新融资新闻）\n4. 排除最近1年内已分析过的公司\n5. 将选中的公司通过微信发送给用户审核：\n   ```python\n   message(action='send', message=f'【AI投资分析】今日推荐分析公司：{company_name}\\n\\n确认分析请回复“批准”，如需更换请回复其他公司名称。')\n   ```\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/company_manager.py`：公司名单管理\n- `references/initial_companies.md`：初始公司名单示例\n\n### 步骤2：五维信息收集\n\n**目标**：从五个维度收集具体、可验证的信息。\n\n**五个维度及收集要点**：\n\n1. **技术**：\n   - 自研能力：查看公司官网、技术博客、GitHub仓库\n   - 数据壁垒：数据来源、数据规模、数据独特性\n   - 专利数：查询专利数据库（中国专利网、USPTO等）\n   - 是否为“套壳”产品：检查核心算法是否原创\n\n2. **增长**：\n   - ARR（年度经常性收入）：查找财务报表、投资者演示稿\n   - 用户增长：月度活跃用户（MAU）、季度增长率\n   - 获客成本（CAC）：市场营销支出/新增客户数\n   - 留存率：用户留存数据（如果有公开数据）\n\n3. **成本**：\n   - 推理成本占收入比重：估算计算资源消耗\n   - 算力储备：GPU数量、云服务合同\n   - 毛利率：收入-成本结构分析\n\n4. **竞争**：\n   - 差异化优势：独特功能、专利技术、商业模式\n   - 客户切换成本：用户迁移难度\n   - 巨头覆盖风险：是否容易被大公司功能更新替代\n\n5. **团队**：\n   - 核心人员背景：创始人、CTO的学术和职业经历\n   - 工程落地经验：团队是否具备产品化能力\n   - 人才结构：科学家 vs. 工程师 vs. 销售比例\n\n**收集工具**：\n- `web_search`：搜索公司信息、新闻、财报\n- `web_fetch`：抓取官网、技术文档\n- `browser`：登录专业数据库（如Crunchbase、PitchBook）\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/research_collector.py`：自动化信息收集脚本\n- `references/evaluation_criteria.md`：五个维度的详细评估标准\n\n### 步骤3：信息可靠性评估\n\n**目标**：对收集的每一条信息进行可信度评级。\n\n**可靠性等级**：\n- **A级（最高）**：官方财务报表、SEC filings、公司官网公告\n- **B级（高）**：权威媒体报道（36氪、钛媒体、TechCrunch）、行业分析报告\n- **C级（中）**：第三方数据平台（天眼查、企查查）、社交媒体官方账号\n- **D级（低）**：匿名爆料、未经证实的传闻\n\n**评估方法**：\n1. 交叉验证：多个独立来源确认同一信息\n2. 时效性：优先使用最近1年内的信息\n3. 来源权威性：优先选择知名媒体、分析师报告\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/reliability_evaluator.py`：自动评估脚本\n- `references/reliability_guidelines.md`：详细评估指南\n\n### 步骤4：资料审核\n\n**目标**：将收集的信息、来源和可信度整理发送给用户审核。\n\n**输出格式**：\n```markdown\n# 【资料审核】{公司名称}信息汇总\n\n## 技术维度\n1. 【A级】自研AI框架：官网显示自研深度学习框架\"NeuroCore\"（来源：官网技术介绍）\n2. 【B级】专利数量：拥有12项机器学习相关专利（来源：中国专利网）\n...\n\n## 增长维度\n...\n```\n\n**交付方式**：通过微信发送完整信息汇总，等待用户确认。\n\n### 步骤5：深度投资分析\n\n**目标**：调用DeepSeek Reasoner模式进行深入分析。\n\n**操作流程**：\n1. 将审核通过的信息整理为上下文\n2. 使用 `sessions_spawn` 创建Reasoner会话：\n   ```python\n   sessions_spawn(\n       runtime='acp',\n       agentId='deepseek-reasoner',\n       task=f'基于以下信息生成AI公司投资分析报告：{context}',\n       model='deepseek/deepseek-reasoner',\n       thinking='on'\n   )\n   ```\n3. 生成报告结构：\n   - 公司概况\n   - 五维深度分析\n   - 风险提示\n   - 投资建议（买入/持有/卖出）\n   - 目标估值区间\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/analysis_generator.py`：报告生成脚本\n- `references/report_template.md`：报告结构模板\n\n### 步骤6：小红书标题生成\n\n**目标**：生成5个专业投研圈视角的爆款标题。\n\n**Prompt模板**：\n```\n请基于这份投资分析报告，为我在小红书（专业投研圈视角）生成5个具有高度专业感、能够吸引投资经理和合伙人点击的标题。\n要求：\n1. 突出核心投资亮点\n2. 使用专业术语但不过于晦涩\n3. 有吸引力的数字和对比\n4. 包含情绪价值词汇\n5. 适合小红书平台风格\n```\n\n**交付方式**：通过微信发送5个标题供用户选择。\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/title_generator.py`：标题生成脚本\n- `references/xhs_title_prompts.md`：标题示例库\n\n### 步骤7：HTML报告渲染\n\n**目标**：将投资分析报告用专业风格排版并渲染为图片。\n\n**操作流程**：\n1. 使用HTML/CSS模板（`assets/report_template.html`）\n2. 将报告内容填充到模板中\n3. 使用浏览器工具渲染并截图：\n   ```python\n   browser(action='open', url='file:///path/to/report.html')\n   browser(action='screenshot', fullPage=True, type='png')\n   ```\n4. 保存图片文件\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/html_renderer.py`：HTML渲染脚本\n- `assets/report_template.html`：报告HTML模板\n- `assets/style.css`：专业投资分析样式\n\n### 步骤8：文案摘要生成\n\n**目标**：生成易读、带emoji的小红书文案摘要。\n\n**要求**：\n- 控制在500字以内\n- 使用适当的emoji增加可读性\n- 突出核心投资观点\n- 适合小红书用户阅读习惯\n\n**示例格式**：\n```\n🚀【AI芯片新贵】深度拆解\n\n📊 技术实力：自研架构，专利护城河\n💰 增长迅猛：ARR年增300%\n⚠️ 风险提示：巨头入场竞争\n...\n```\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/summary_tag_generator.py`：摘要生成脚本\n\n### 步骤9：标签生成与交付\n\n**目标**：生成5个相关标签并交付最终成果。\n\n**标签要求**：\n- 涵盖公司领域、技术方向、投资阶段\n- 适合小红书话题标签\n- 有搜索热度\n\n**最终交付物**：\n1. 选定的标题\n2. 渲染后的报告图片\n3. 文案摘要\n4. 5个相关标签\n\n**交付方式**：通过微信一次性发送所有成果。"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":586,"output":2078,"cacheRead":25856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28520,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776130220689,"responseId":"d8bca61b-e546-40e4-8b47-ad1fd356805a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c07ef66","parentId":"6bd06404","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:31:19.805Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_9LjkQ11piX62UDFHxoZhjRNc","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/SKILL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  26 ## 详细工作流程\n  27 \n  28 ## [TODO: Replace with the first main section based on chosen structure]\n  29 \n- 30 [TODO: Add content here. See examples in existing skills:\n- 31 - Code samples for technical skills\n- 32 - Decision trees for complex workflows\n- 33 - Concrete examples with realistic user requests\n- 34 - References to scripts/templates/references as needed]\n+ 30 ### 步骤1：公司选择与审核\n  35 \n+ 32 **目标**：从AI科技公司名单中选择一家尚未分析或超过1年未分析的公司。\n+ 33 \n+ 34 **操作流程**：\n+ 35 1. 检查 `memory/companies.json` 文件（如果不存在则创建初始名单）\n+ 36 2. 初始名单条件：至少完成A轮融资的AI科技公司\n+ 37 3. 每日检查是否有新公司可加入（通过web_search搜索最新融资新闻）\n+ 38 4. 排除最近1年内已分析过的公司\n+ 39 5. 将选中的公司通过微信发送给用户审核：\n+ 40    ```python\n+ 41    message(action='send', message=f'【AI投资分析】今日推荐分析公司：{company_name}\\n\\n确认分析请回复“批准”，如需更换请回复其他公司名称。')\n+ 42    ```\n+ 43 \n+ 44 **关键文件**：\n+ 45 - `scripts/company_manager.py`：公司名单管理\n+ 46 - `references/initial_companies.md`：初始公司名单示例\n+ 47 \n+ 48 ### 步骤2：五维信息收集\n+ 49 \n+ 50 **目标**：从五个维度收集具体、可验证的信息。\n+ 51 \n+ 52 **五个维度及收集要点**：\n+ 53 \n+ 54 1. **技术**：\n+ 55    - 自研能力：查看公司官网、技术博客、GitHub仓库\n+ 56    - 数据壁垒：数据来源、数据规模、数据独特性\n+ 57    - 专利数：查询专利数据库（中国专利网、USPTO等）\n+ 58    - 是否为“套壳”产品：检查核心算法是否原创\n+ 59 \n+ 60 2. **增长**：\n+ 61    - ARR（年度经常性收入）：查找财务报表、投资者演示稿\n+ 62    - 用户增长：月度活跃用户（MAU）、季度增长率\n+ 63    - 获客成本（CAC）：市场营销支出/新增客户数\n+ 64    - 留存率：用户留存数据（如果有公开数据）\n+ 65 \n+ 66 3. **成本**：\n+ 67    - 推理成本占收入比重：估算计算资源消耗\n+ 68    - 算力储备：GPU数量、云服务合同\n+ 69    - 毛利率：收入-成本结构分析\n+ 70 \n+ 71 4. **竞争**：\n+ 72    - 差异化优势：独特功能、专利技术、商业模式\n+ 73    - 客户切换成本：用户迁移难度\n+ 74    - 巨头覆盖风险：是否容易被大公司功能更新替代\n+ 75 \n+ 76 5. **团队**：\n+ 77    - 核心人员背景：创始人、CTO的学术和职业经历\n+ 78    - 工程落地经验：团队是否具备产品化能力\n+ 79    - 人才结构：科学家 vs. 工程师 vs. 销售比例\n+ 80 \n+ 81 **收集工具**：\n+ 82 - `web_search`：搜索公司信息、新闻、财报\n+ 83 - `web_fetch`：抓取官网、技术文档\n+ 84 - `browser`：登录专业数据库（如Crunchbase、PitchBook）\n+ 85 \n+ 86 **关键文件**：\n+ 87 - `scripts/research_collector.py`：自动化信息收集脚本\n+ 88 - `references/evaluation_criteria.md`：五个维度的详细评估标准\n+ 89 \n+ 90 ### 步骤3：信息可靠性评估\n+ 91 \n+ 92 **目标**：对收集的每一条信息进行可信度评级。\n+ 93 \n+ 94 **可靠性等级**：\n+ 95 - **A级（最高）**：官方财务报表、SEC filings、公司官网公告\n+ 96 - **B级（高）**：权威媒体报道（36氪、钛媒体、TechCrunch）、行业分析报告\n+ 97 - **C级（中）**：第三方数据平台（天眼查、企查查）、社交媒体官方账号\n+ 98 - **D级（低）**：匿名爆料、未经证实的传闻\n+ 99 \n+100 **评估方法**：\n+101 1. 交叉验证：多个独立来源确认同一信息\n+102 2. 时效性：优先使用最近1年内的信息\n+103 3. 来源权威性：优先选择知名媒体、分析师报告\n+104 \n+105 **关键文件**：\n+106 - `scripts/reliability_evaluator.py`：自动评估脚本\n+107 - `references/reliability_guidelines.md`：详细评估指南\n+108 \n+109 ### 步骤4：资料审核\n+110 \n+111 **目标**：将收集的信息、来源和可信度整理发送给用户审核。\n+112 \n+113 **输出格式**：\n+114 ```markdown\n+115 # 【资料审核】{公司名称}信息汇总\n+116 \n+117 ## 技术维度\n+118 1. 【A级】自研AI框架：官网显示自研深度学习框架\"NeuroCore\"（来源：官网技术介绍）\n+119 2. 【B级】专利数量：拥有12项机器学习相关专利（来源：中国专利网）\n+120 ...\n+121 \n+122 ## 增长维度\n+123 ...\n+124 ```\n+125 \n+126 **交付方式**：通过微信发送完整信息汇总，等待用户确认。\n+127 \n+128 ### 步骤5：深度投资分析\n+129 \n+130 **目标**：调用DeepSeek Reasoner模式进行深入分析。\n+131 \n+132 **操作流程**：\n+133 1. 将审核通过的信息整理为上下文\n+134 2. 使用 `sessions_spawn` 创建Reasoner会话：\n+135    ```python\n+136    sessions_spawn(\n+137        runtime='acp',\n+138        agentId='deepseek-reasoner',\n+139        task=f'基于以下信息生成AI公司投资分析报告：{context}',\n+140        model='deepseek/deepseek-reasoner',\n+141        thinking='on'\n+142    )\n+143    ```\n+144 3. 生成报告结构：\n+145    - 公司概况\n+146    - 五维深度分析\n+147    - 风险提示\n+148    - 投资建议（买入/持有/卖出）\n+149    - 目标估值区间\n+150 \n+151 **关键文件**：\n+152 - `scripts/analysis_generator.py`：报告生成脚本\n+153 - `references/report_template.md`：报告结构模板\n+154 \n+155 ### 步骤6：小红书标题生成\n+156 \n+157 **目标**：生成5个专业投研圈视角的爆款标题。\n+158 \n+159 **Prompt模板**：\n+160 ```\n+161 请基于这份投资分析报告，为我在小红书（专业投研圈视角）生成5个具有高度专业感、能够吸引投资经理和合伙人点击的标题。\n+162 要求：\n+163 1. 突出核心投资亮点\n+164 2. 使用专业术语但不过于晦涩\n+165 3. 有吸引力的数字和对比\n+166 4. 包含情绪价值词汇\n+167 5. 适合小红书平台风格\n+168 ```\n+169 \n+170 **交付方式**：通过微信发送5个标题供用户选择。\n+171 \n+172 **关键文件**：\n+173 - `scripts/title_generator.py`：标题生成脚本\n+174 - `references/xhs_title_prompts.md`：标题示例库\n+175 \n+176 ### 步骤7：HTML报告渲染\n+177 \n+178 **目标**：将投资分析报告用专业风格排版并渲染为图片。\n+179 \n+180 **操作流程**：\n+181 1. 使用HTML/CSS模板（`assets/report_template.html`）\n+182 2. 将报告内容填充到模板中\n+183 3. 使用浏览器工具渲染并截图：\n+184    ```python\n+185    browser(action='open', url='file:///path/to/report.html')\n+186    browser(action='screenshot', fullPage=True, type='png')\n+187    ```\n+188 4. 保存图片文件\n+189 \n+190 **关键文件**：\n+191 - `scripts/html_renderer.py`：HTML渲染脚本\n+192 - `assets/report_template.html`：报告HTML模板\n+193 - `assets/style.css`：专业投资分析样式\n+194 \n+195 ### 步骤8：文案摘要生成\n+196 \n+197 **目标**：生成易读、带emoji的小红书文案摘要。\n+198 \n+199 **要求**：\n+200 - 控制在500字以内\n+201 - 使用适当的emoji增加可读性\n+202 - 突出核心投资观点\n+203 - 适合小红书用户阅读习惯\n+204 \n+205 **示例格式**：\n+206 ```\n+207 🚀【AI芯片新贵】深度拆解\n+208 \n+209 📊 技术实力：自研架构，专利护城河\n+210 💰 增长迅猛：ARR年增300%\n+211 ⚠️ 风险提示：巨头入场竞争\n+212 ...\n+213 ```\n+214 \n+215 **关键文件**：\n+216 - `scripts/summary_tag_generator.py`：摘要生成脚本\n+217 \n+218 ### 步骤9：标签生成与交付\n+219 \n+220 **目标**：生成5个相关标签并交付最终成果。\n+221 \n+222 **标签要求**：\n+223 - 涵盖公司领域、技术方向、投资阶段\n+224 - 适合小红书话题标签\n+225 - 有搜索热度\n+226 \n+227 **最终交付物**：\n+228 1. 选定的标题\n+229 2. 渲染后的报告图片\n+230 3. 文案摘要\n+231 4. 5个相关标签\n+232 \n+233 **交付方式**：通过微信一次性发送所有成果。\n+234 \n  36 ## Resources (optional)\n  37 \n  38 Create only the resource directories this skill actually needs. Delete this section if no resources are required.\n  39 \n     ...","firstChangedLine":30},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776130279805}}
{"type":"message","id":"180a4240","parentId":"1c07ef66","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:31:53.110Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要更新Resources部分，删除通用描述，改为具体说明本技能需要的资源。先看看Resources部分的内容。然后替换掉。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_X1MgGkP9fSshpvUCenOXLiBN","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Resources (optional)\n\nCreate only the resource directories this skill actually needs. Delete this section if no resources are required.\n\n### scripts/\nExecutable code (Python/Bash/etc.) that can be run directly to perform specific operations.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- PDF skill: `fill_fillable_fields.py`, `extract_form_field_info.py` - utilities for PDF manipulation\n- DOCX skill: `document.py`, `utilities.py` - Python modules for document processing\n\n**Appropriate for:** Python scripts, shell scripts, any executable code that performs automation, data processing, or specific operations.\n\n**Note:** Scripts may be executed without loading into context, but can still be read by Codex for patching or environment adjustments.\n\n### references/\nDocumentation and reference material intended to be loaded into context to inform Codex's process and thinking.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- Product management: `communication.md`, `context_building.md` - detailed workflow guides\n- BigQuery: API reference documentation and query examples\n- Finance: Schema documentation, company policies\n\n**Appropriate for:** In-depth documentation, API references, database schemas, comprehensive guides, or any detailed information that Codex should reference while working.\n\n### assets/\nFiles not intended to be loaded into context, but rather used within the output Codex produces.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- Brand styling: PowerPoint template files (.pptx), logo files\n- Frontend builder: HTML/React boilerplate project directories\n- Typography: Font files (.ttf, .woff2)\n\n**Appropriate for:** Templates, boilerplate code, document templates, images, icons, fonts, or any files meant to be copied or used in the final output.\n\n---\n\n**Not every skill requires all three types of resources.**","newText":"## 资源文件说明\n\n本技能包含以下资源文件，用于支持完整的自动化流程：\n\n### scripts/ 脚本目录\n\n包含执行具体任务的Python脚本：\n\n1. `company_manager.py` - 公司名单管理\n   - 功能：读取/更新公司名单，检查重复，添加新公司\n   - 数据结构：JSON格式，包含公司名称、分析日期、融资阶段等\n\n2. `research_collector.py` - 五维信息收集\n   - 功能：自动化搜索五个维度的信息，整理为结构化数据\n   - 依赖：web_search, web_fetch, browser工具\n\n3. `reliability_evaluator.py` - 信息可靠性评估\n   - 功能：根据来源类型自动评级，支持交叉验证\n\n4. `analysis_generator.py` - 深度投资分析生成\n   - 功能：调用DeepSeek Reasoner模式，生成专业投资报告\n   - 接口：sessions_spawn with runtime='acp'\n\n5. `title_generator.py` - 小红书标题生成\n   - 功能：基于报告内容生成5个爆款标题\n   - 模板：使用预定义的prompt模板\n\n6. `html_renderer.py` - HTML报告渲染\n   - 功能：将报告填充到HTML模板，使用浏览器渲染截图\n\n7. `summary_tag_generator.py` - 摘要和标签生成\n   - 功能：生成小红书文案摘要和5个相关标签\n\n### references/ 参考文档\n\n包含详细的标准和模板：\n\n1. `evaluation_criteria.md` - 五个维度的详细评估标准\n   - 每个维度的具体指标、数据来源建议、评估方法\n\n2. `reliability_guidelines.md` - 信息可靠性评估指南\n   - 可靠性等级定义、交叉验证方法、时效性要求\n\n3. `report_template.md` - 投资分析报告结构模板\n   - 报告章节结构、内容要求、格式规范\n\n4. `xhs_title_prompts.md` - 小红书标题生成prompt库\n   - 多种风格的标题模板和成功案例\n\n5. `html_template.md` - HTML/CSS模板参考\n   - 模板变量说明、样式定制指南\n\n### assets/ 资产文件\n\n包含输出所需的模板和样式：\n\n1. `report_template.html` - 投资分析报告HTML模板\n   - 专业投资分析风格，响应式设计\n\n2. `style.css` - 报告样式表\n   - 字体、颜色、布局等视觉样式\n\n3. `initial_companies.json` - 初始公司名单\n   - 至少完成A轮融资的AI科技公司示例列表"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":2109,"output":1152,"cacheRead":26432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29693,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776130279806,"responseId":"51de29e9-bb8e-42c0-aab3-800c5223e391"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c106001b","parentId":"180a4240","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:31:53.124Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_X1MgGkP9fSshpvUCenOXLiBN","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in /root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/SKILL.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n---\\nname: investment-xhs\\ndescription: 完全自主的小红书投资分析报告内容策划。为每天一家AI科技公司生成深度投资分析报告，涵盖技术、增长、成本、竞争、团队五个维度，并生成小红书爆款标题、HTML渲染报告、文案摘要和标签。触发条件：当用户提到“小红书投资分析报告内容策划”、“AI科技公司投资分析”、“生成投资分析报告”或类似请求时使用此技能。\\n---\\n\\n# Investment XHS - 小红书投资分析报告内容策划\\n\\n## 概述\\n\\n本技能实现完全自主的小红书投资分析报告内容策划流水线。每天自动选择一家AI科技公司，从五个维度（技术、增长、成本、竞争、团队）收集信息，评估可靠性，生成深度投资分析报告，并转化为小红书平台适用的标题、图片、摘要和标签。\\n\\n## 工作流概览\\n\\n完整的SOP包含9个步骤，每一步都需要人工审核以确保质量：\\n\\n1. **公司选择与审核**：从维护的AI科技公司名单中选取一家，通过微信发送给用户审核\\n2. **五维信息收集**：从技术、增长、成本、竞争、团队五个角度搜集具体依据\\n3. **信息可靠性评估**：对搜集的信息进行可信度评级\\n4. **资料审核**：将搜集的信息、来源和可信度发送给用户二次审核\\n5. **深度投资分析**：调用DeepSeek Reasoner模式生成投资分析报告\\n6. **小红书标题生成**：基于报告生成5个专业投研圈视角的爆款标题\\n7. **HTML报告渲染**：将报告用专业投资分析风格排版并渲染为图片\\n8. **文案摘要生成**：生成易读、带emoji的小红书文案摘要\\n9. **标签生成与交付**：生成5个相关标签，交付标题、图片、摘要、标签\\n\\n## 详细工作流程\\n\\n## [TODO: Replace with the first main section based on chosen \\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in /root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/SKILL.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n---\nname: investment-xhs\ndescription: 完全自主的小红书投资分析报告内容策划。为每天一家AI科技公司生成深度投资分析报告，涵盖技术、增长、成本、竞争、团队五个维度，并生成小红书爆款标题、HTML渲染报告、文案摘要和标签。触发条件：当用户提到“小红书投资分析报告内容策划”、“AI科技公司投资分析”、“生成投资分析报告”或类似请求时使用此技能。\n---\n\n# Investment XHS - 小红书投资分析报告内容策划\n\n## 概述\n\n本技能实现完全自主的小红书投资分析报告内容策划流水线。每天自动选择一家AI科技公司，从五个维度（技术、增长、成本、竞争、团队）收集信息，评估可靠性，生成深度投资分析报告，并转化为小红书平台适用的标题、图片、摘要和标签。\n\n## 工作流概览\n\n完整的SOP包含9个步骤，每一步都需要人工审核以确保质量：\n\n1. **公司选择与审核**：从维护的AI科技公司名单中选取一家，通过微信发送给用户审核\n2. **五维信息收集**：从技术、增长、成本、竞争、团队五个角度搜集具体依据\n3. **信息可靠性评估**：对搜集的信息进行可信度评级\n4. **资料审核**：将搜集的信息、来源和可信度发送给用户二次审核\n5. **深度投资分析**：调用DeepSeek Reasoner模式生成投资分析报告\n6. **小红书标题生成**：基于报告生成5个专业投研圈视角的爆款标题\n7. **HTML报告渲染**：将报告用专业投资分析风格排版并渲染为图片\n8. **文案摘要生成**：生成易读、带emoji的小红书文案摘要\n9. **标签生成与交付**：生成5个相关标签，交付标题、图片、摘要、标签\n\n## 详细工作流程\n\n## [TODO: Replace with the first main section based on chosen \n... (truncated)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776130313123}}
{"type":"message","id":"41760c8e","parentId":"c106001b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:31:57.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要先读取文件内容，看看Resources部分的确切文本。让我先读取文件尾部。用read查看。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_L1DsJlSMpDrVSB6RA8EJWxdR","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/SKILL.md","offset":80}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":1713,"output":125,"cacheRead":28480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30318,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776130313125,"responseId":"9713e130-821c-4e31-802b-9f2318dde13d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9715464f","parentId":"41760c8e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:31:57.184Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_L1DsJlSMpDrVSB6RA8EJWxdR","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n**收集工具**：\n- `web_search`：搜索公司信息、新闻、财报\n- `web_fetch`：抓取官网、技术文档\n- `browser`：登录专业数据库（如Crunchbase、PitchBook）\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/research_collector.py`：自动化信息收集脚本\n- `references/evaluation_criteria.md`：五个维度的详细评估标准\n\n### 步骤3：信息可靠性评估\n\n**目标**：对收集的每一条信息进行可信度评级。\n\n**可靠性等级**：\n- **A级（最高）**：官方财务报表、SEC filings、公司官网公告\n- **B级（高）**：权威媒体报道（36氪、钛媒体、TechCrunch）、行业分析报告\n- **C级（中）**：第三方数据平台（天眼查、企查查）、社交媒体官方账号\n- **D级（低）**：匿名爆料、未经证实的传闻\n\n**评估方法**：\n1. 交叉验证：多个独立来源确认同一信息\n2. 时效性：优先使用最近1年内的信息\n3. 来源权威性：优先选择知名媒体、分析师报告\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/reliability_evaluator.py`：自动评估脚本\n- `references/reliability_guidelines.md`：详细评估指南\n\n### 步骤4：资料审核\n\n**目标**：将收集的信息、来源和可信度整理发送给用户审核。\n\n**输出格式**：\n```markdown\n# 【资料审核】{公司名称}信息汇总\n\n## 技术维度\n1. 【A级】自研AI框架：官网显示自研深度学习框架\"NeuroCore\"（来源：官网技术介绍）\n2. 【B级】专利数量：拥有12项机器学习相关专利（来源：中国专利网）\n...\n\n## 增长维度\n...\n```\n\n**交付方式**：通过微信发送完整信息汇总，等待用户确认。\n\n### 步骤5：深度投资分析\n\n**目标**：调用DeepSeek Reasoner模式进行深入分析。\n\n**操作流程**：\n1. 将审核通过的信息整理为上下文\n2. 使用 `sessions_spawn` 创建Reasoner会话：\n   ```python\n   sessions_spawn(\n       runtime='acp',\n       agentId='deepseek-reasoner',\n       task=f'基于以下信息生成AI公司投资分析报告：{context}',\n       model='deepseek/deepseek-reasoner',\n       thinking='on'\n   )\n   ```\n3. 生成报告结构：\n   - 公司概况\n   - 五维深度分析\n   - 风险提示\n   - 投资建议（买入/持有/卖出）\n   - 目标估值区间\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/analysis_generator.py`：报告生成脚本\n- `references/report_template.md`：报告结构模板\n\n### 步骤6：小红书标题生成\n\n**目标**：生成5个专业投研圈视角的爆款标题。\n\n**Prompt模板**：\n```\n请基于这份投资分析报告，为我在小红书（专业投研圈视角）生成5个具有高度专业感、能够吸引投资经理和合伙人点击的标题。\n要求：\n1. 突出核心投资亮点\n2. 使用专业术语但不过于晦涩\n3. 有吸引力的数字和对比\n4. 包含情绪价值词汇\n5. 适合小红书平台风格\n```\n\n**交付方式**：通过微信发送5个标题供用户选择。\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/title_generator.py`：标题生成脚本\n- `references/xhs_title_prompts.md`：标题示例库\n\n### 步骤7：HTML报告渲染\n\n**目标**：将投资分析报告用专业风格排版并渲染为图片。\n\n**操作流程**：\n1. 使用HTML/CSS模板（`assets/report_template.html`）\n2. 将报告内容填充到模板中\n3. 使用浏览器工具渲染并截图：\n   ```python\n   browser(action='open', url='file:///path/to/report.html')\n   browser(action='screenshot', fullPage=True, type='png')\n   ```\n4. 保存图片文件\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/html_renderer.py`：HTML渲染脚本\n- `assets/report_template.html`：报告HTML模板\n- `assets/style.css`：专业投资分析样式\n\n### 步骤8：文案摘要生成\n\n**目标**：生成易读、带emoji的小红书文案摘要。\n\n**要求**：\n- 控制在500字以内\n- 使用适当的emoji增加可读性\n- 突出核心投资观点\n- 适合小红书用户阅读习惯\n\n**示例格式**：\n```\n🚀【AI芯片新贵】深度拆解\n\n📊 技术实力：自研架构，专利护城河\n💰 增长迅猛：ARR年增300%\n⚠️ 风险提示：巨头入场竞争\n...\n```\n\n**关键文件**：\n- `scripts/summary_tag_generator.py`：摘要生成脚本\n\n### 步骤9：标签生成与交付\n\n**目标**：生成5个相关标签并交付最终成果。\n\n**标签要求**：\n- 涵盖公司领域、技术方向、投资阶段\n- 适合小红书话题标签\n- 有搜索热度\n\n**最终交付物**：\n1. 选定的标题\n2. 渲染后的报告图片\n3. 文案摘要\n4. 5个相关标签\n\n**交付方式**：通过微信一次性发送所有成果。\n\n## Resources (optional)\n\nCreate only the resource directories this skill actually needs. Delete this section if no resources are required.\n\n### scripts/\nExecutable code (Python/Bash/etc.) that can be run directly to perform specific operations.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- PDF skill: `fill_fillable_fields.py`, `extract_form_field_info.py` - utilities for PDF manipulation\n- DOCX skill: `document.py`, `utilities.py` - Python modules for document processing\n\n**Appropriate for:** Python scripts, shell scripts, or any executable code that performs automation, data processing, or specific operations.\n\n**Note:** Scripts may be executed without loading into context, but can still be read by Codex for patching or environment adjustments.\n\n### references/\nDocumentation and reference material intended to be loaded into context to inform Codex's process and thinking.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- Product management: `communication.md`, `context_building.md` - detailed workflow guides\n- BigQuery: API reference documentation and query examples\n- Finance: Schema documentation, company policies\n\n**Appropriate for:** In-depth documentation, API references, database schemas, comprehensive guides, or any detailed information that Codex should reference while working.\n\n### assets/\nFiles not intended to be loaded into context, but rather used within the output Codex produces.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- Brand styling: PowerPoint template files (.pptx), logo files\n- Frontend builder: HTML/React boilerplate project directories\n- Typography: Font files (.ttf, .woff2)\n\n**Appropriate for:** Templates, boilerplate code, document templates, images, icons, fonts, or any files meant to be copied or used in the final output.\n\n---\n\n**Not every skill requires all three types of resources.**\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776130317184}}
{"type":"message","id":"13847c5d","parentId":"9715464f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:32:29.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到了Resources部分的确切文本。我需要替换从“## Resources (optional)”开始一直到文件末尾的部分。让我精确替换。使用编辑工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2WXDwMcUoCJC6qkSZg4rMKaR","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Resources (optional)\n\nCreate only the resource directories this skill actually needs. Delete this section if no resources are required.\n\n### scripts/\nExecutable code (Python/Bash/etc.) that can be run directly to perform specific operations.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- PDF skill: `fill_fillable_fields.py`, `extract_form_field_info.py` - utilities for PDF manipulation\n- DOCX skill: `document.py`, `utilities.py` - Python modules for document processing\n\n**Appropriate for:** Python scripts, shell scripts, or any executable code that performs automation, data processing, or specific operations.\n\n**Note:** Scripts may be executed without loading into context, but can still be read by Codex for patching or environment adjustments.\n\n### references/\nDocumentation and reference material intended to be loaded into context to inform Codex's process and thinking.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- Product management: `communication.md`, `context_building.md` - detailed workflow guides\n- BigQuery: API reference documentation and query examples\n- Finance: Schema documentation, company policies\n\n**Appropriate for:** In-depth documentation, API references, database schemas, comprehensive guides, or any detailed information that Codex should reference while working.\n\n### assets/\nFiles not intended to be loaded into context, but rather used within the output Codex produces.\n\n**Examples from other skills:**\n- Brand styling: PowerPoint template files (.pptx), logo files\n- Frontend builder: HTML/React boilerplate project directories\n- Typography: Font files (.ttf, .woff2)\n\n**Appropriate for:** Templates, boilerplate code, document templates, images, icons, fonts, or any files meant to be copied or used in the final output.\n\n---\n\n**Not every skill requires all three types of resources.**","newText":"## 资源文件说明\n\n本技能包含以下资源文件，用于支持完整的自动化流程：\n\n### scripts/ 脚本目录\n\n包含执行具体任务的Python脚本：\n\n1. `company_manager.py` - 公司名单管理\n   - 功能：读取/更新公司名单，检查重复，添加新公司\n   - 数据结构：JSON格式，包含公司名称、分析日期、融资阶段等\n\n2. `research_collector.py` - 五维信息收集\n   - 功能：自动化搜索五个维度的信息，整理为结构化数据\n   - 依赖：web_search, web_fetch, browser工具\n\n3. `reliability_evaluator.py` - 信息可靠性评估\n   - 功能：根据来源类型自动评级，支持交叉验证\n\n4. `analysis_generator.py` - 深度投资分析生成\n   - 功能：调用DeepSeek Reasoner模式，生成专业投资报告\n   - 接口：sessions_spawn with runtime='acp'\n\n5. `title_generator.py` - 小红书标题生成\n   - 功能：基于报告内容生成5个爆款标题\n   - 模板：使用预定义的prompt模板\n\n6. `html_renderer.py` - HTML报告渲染\n   - 功能：将报告填充到HTML模板，使用浏览器渲染截图\n\n7. `summary_tag_generator.py` - 摘要和标签生成\n   - 功能：生成小红书文案摘要和5个相关标签\n\n### references/ 参考文档\n\n包含详细的标准和模板：\n\n1. `evaluation_criteria.md` - 五个维度的详细评估标准\n   - 每个维度的具体指标、数据来源建议、评估方法\n\n2. `reliability_guidelines.md` - 信息可靠性评估指南\n   - 可靠性等级定义、交叉验证方法、时效性要求\n\n3. `report_template.md` - 投资分析报告结构模板\n   - 报告章节结构、内容要求、格式规范\n\n4. `xhs_title_prompts.md` - 小红书标题生成prompt库\n   - 多种风格的标题模板和成功案例\n\n5. `html_template.md` - HTML/CSS模板参考\n   - 模板变量说明、样式定制指南\n\n### assets/ 资产文件\n\n包含输出所需的模板和样式：\n\n1. `report_template.html` - 投资分析报告HTML模板\n   - 专业投资分析风格，响应式设计\n\n2. `style.css` - 报告样式表\n   - 字体、颜色、布局等视觉样式\n\n3. `initial_companies.json` - 初始公司名单\n   - 至少完成A轮融资的AI科技公司示例列表"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":1722,"output":1159,"cacheRead":30144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33025,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776130317185,"responseId":"e0f45927-b692-40c9-9e65-b300a65d7490"}}
