examples\n-256 - Finance: Schema documentation, company policies\n+254 4. `analysis_generator.py` - 深度投资分析生成\n+255    - 功能：调用DeepSeek Reasoner模式，生成专业投资报告\n+256    - 接口：sessions_spawn with runtime='acp'\n 257 \n-258 **Appropriate for:** In-depth documentation, API references, database schemas, comprehensive guides, or any detailed information that Codex should reference while working.\n+258 5. `title_generator.py` - 小红书标题生成\n+259    - 功能：基于报告内容生成5个爆款标题\n+260    - 模板：使用预定义的prompt模板\n 259 \n-260 ### assets/\n-261 Files not intended to be loaded into context, but rather used within the output Codex produces.\n+262 6. `html_renderer.py` - HTML报告渲染\n+263    - 功能：将报告填充到HTML模板，使用浏览器渲染截图\n 262 \n-263 **Examples from other skills:**\n-264 - Brand styling: PowerPoint template files (.pptx), logo files\n-265 - Frontend builder: HTML/React boilerplate project directories\n-266 - Typography: Font files (.ttf, .woff2)\n+265 7. `summary_tag_generator.py` - 摘要和标签生成\n+266    - 功能：生成小红书文案摘要和5个相关标签\n 267 \n-268 **Appropriate for:** Templates, boilerplate code, document templates, images, icons, fonts, or any files meant to be copied or used in the final output.\n+268 ### references/ 参考文档\n 269 \n-270 ---\n+270 包含详细的标准和模板：\n 271 \n-272 **Not every skill requires all three types of resources.**\n+272 1. `evaluation_criteria.md` - 五个维度的详细评估标准\n+273    - 每个维度的具体指标、数据来源建议、评估方法\n+274 \n+275 2. `reliability_guidelines.md` - 信息可靠性评估指南\n+276    - 可靠性等级定义、交叉验证方法、时效性要求\n+277 \n+278 3. `report_template.md` - 投资分析报告结构模板\n+279    - 报告章节结构、内容要求、格式规范\n+280 \n+281 4. `xhs_title_prompts.md` - 小红书标题生成prompt库\n+282    - 多种风格的标题模板和成功案例\n+283 \n+284 5. `html_template.md` - HTML/CSS模板参考\n+285    - 模板变量说明、样式定制指南\n+286 \n+287 ### assets/ 资产文件\n+288 \n+289 包含输出所需的模板和样式：\n+290 \n+291 1. `report_template.html` - 投资分析报告HTML模板\n+292    - 专业投资分析风格，响应式设计\n+293 \n+294 2. `style.css` - 报告样式表\n+295    - 字体、颜色、布局等视觉样式\n+296 \n+297 3. `initial_companies.json` - 初始公司名单\n+298    - 至少完成A轮融资的AI科技公司示例列表","firstChangedLine":235