{"type":"message","id":"b0425ebc","parentId":"ab0cdeb0","timestamp":"2026-04-14T01:38:36.299Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"assets目录是空的。现在创建report_template.html。我将从html_template.md中提取HTML模板内容。实际上，html_template.md中已经包含了完整的HTML和CSS。但为了结构清晰，我应该将HTML和CSS分开存放。先创建report_template.html，包含HTML结构。使用write工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5Cksc8UGt7sud0g3glCOFeJJ","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/assets/report_template.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>{company_name} - AI投资分析报告</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Source+Code+Pro:wght@400;500&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 报告容器 -->\n    <div class=\"report-container\">\n        <!-- 封面页 -->\n        <div class=\"page cover-page\">\n            <div class=\"cover-content\">\n                <div class=\"cover-badge\">AI投资分析报告</div>\n                <h1 class=\"company-name\">{company_name}</h1>\n                <div class=\"cover-subtitle\">深度五维分析报告</div>\n                \n                <div class=\"cover-metrics\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-item\">\n                        <div class=\"metric-value\">{investment_rating}</div>\n                        <div class=\"metric-label\">投资评级</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-item\">\n                        <div class=\"metric-value\">{target_valuation}</div>\n                        <div class=\"metric-label\">目标估值</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-item\">\n                        <div class=\"metric-value\">{industry_rank}</div>\n                        <div class=\"metric-label\">行业排名</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"cover-footer\">\n                    <div class=\"report-date\">报告日期：{report_date}</div>\n                    <div class=\"analyst-name\">分析师：OpenClaw Investment Research</div>\n                    <div class=\"disclaimer\">本报告仅供参考，不构成投资建议</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 执行摘要 -->\n        <div class=\"page summary-page\">\n            <h2><i class=\"fas fa-bullseye\"></i> 执行摘要</h2>\n            <div class=\"executive-summary\">\n                {executive_summary}\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"key-metrics-grid\">\n                <div class=\"metric-card {tech_score_class}\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-title\">技术评分</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-value\">{tech_score}/10</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-desc\">{tech_highlight}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"metric-card {growth_score_class}\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-title\">增长评分</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-value\">{growth_score}/10</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-desc\">{growth_highlight}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"metric-card {cost_score_class}\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-title\">成本评分</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-value\">{cost_score}/10</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-desc\">{cost_assessment}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"metric-card {competition_score_class}\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-title\">竞争评分</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-value\">{competition_score}/10</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-desc\">{competitive_advantage}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"metric-card {team_score_class}\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-title\">团队评分</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-value\">{team_score}/10</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-desc\">{team_highlight}</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 五维分析详情 -->\n        <div class=\"page analysis-page\">\n            <h2><i class=\"fas fa-chart-network\"></i> 五维深度分析</h2>\n            \n            <!-- 技术维度 -->\n            <div class=\"dimension-section\" id=\"technology\">\n                <h3><span class=\"dimension-icon\">🔬</span> 技术维度</h3>\n                <div class=\"dimension-content\">\n                    {technology_content}\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"reliability-badge reliability-{tech_reliability}\">可靠性：{tech_reliability_label}</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- 增长维度 -->\n            <div class=\"dimension-section\" id=\"growth\">\n                <h3><span class=\"dimension-icon\">📈</span> 增长维度</h3>\n                <div class=\"dimension-content\">\n                    {growth_content}\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"reliability-badge reliability-{growth_reliability}\">可靠性：{growth_reliability_label}</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- 成本维度 -->\n            <div class=\"dimension-section\" id=\"cost\">\n                <h3><span class=\"dimension-icon\">💰</span> 成本维度</h3>\n                <div class=\"dimension-content\">\n                    {cost_content}\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"reliability-badge reliability-{cost_reliability}\">可靠性：{cost_reliability_label}</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- 竞争维度 -->\n            <div class=\"dimension-section\" id=\"competition\">\n                <h3><span class=\"dimension-icon\">⚔️</span> 竞争维度</h3>\n                <div class=\"dimension-content\">\n                    {competition_content}\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"reliability-badge reliability-{competition_reliability}\">可靠性：{competition_reliability_label}</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- 团队维度 -->\n            <div class=\"dimension-section\" id=\"team\">\n                <h3><span class=\"dimension-icon\">👥</span> 团队维度</h3>\n                <div class=\"dimension-content\">\n                    {team_content}\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"reliability-badge reliability-{team_reliability}\">可靠性：{team_reliability_label}</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 投资建议 -->\n        <div class=\"page recommendation-page\">\n            <h2><i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i> 投资建议</h2>\n            \n            <div class=\"recommendation-card {rating_class}\">\n                <div class=\"recommendation-header\">\n                    <div class=\"recommendation-title\">{investment_rating}</div>\n                    <div class=\"recommendation-subtitle\">{rating_explanation}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"recommendation-body\">\n                    {recommendation_content}\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"risk-section\">\n                <h4><i class=\"fas fa-exclamation-triangle\"></i> 风险提示</h4>\n                <ul class=\"risk-list\">\n                    {risk_items}\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 附录 -->\n        <div class=\"page appendix-page\">\n            <h2><i class=\"fas fa-paperclip\"></i> 附录</h2>\n            \n            <div class=\"appendix-section\">\n                <h4>信息可靠性评估</h4>\n                <table class=\"reliability-table\">\n                    <thead>\n                        <tr>\n                            <th>信息类别</th>\n                            <th>来源</th>\n                            <th>可靠性等级</th>\n                            <th>验证方法</th>\n                        </tr>\n                    </thead>\n                    <tbody>\n                        {reliability_table_rows}\n                    </tbody>\n                </table>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"disclaimer-section\">\n                <h4>免责声明</h4>\n                <p>1. 本报告基于公开信息分析，仅供参考。</p>\n                <p>2. 分析结果不构成投资建议，投资者需独立判断。</p>\n                <p>3. 市场有风险，投资需谨慎。</p>\n                <p>4. 报告日期：{report_date}，信息可能随时间变化。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":202,"output":2008,"cacheRead":44352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46562,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776130663732,"responseId":"0d947aa0-a575-4ea4-af97-346cda70ab1e"}}
