{"type":"message","id":"4707418b","parentId":"c22f7f39","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:35:33.033Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文件内容看起来正确。现在我需要生成审核格式的消息。我可以写一个简单的Python代码来格式化，或者直接使用research_collector.py脚本的输出。前面运行research_collector.py时已经看到了format_for_review的输出。让我直接使用那个输出。\n\n实际上，我可以再次运行research_collector.py并捕获其format_for_review输出。但更好的方法是直接生成审核消息，因为研究数据文件已经存在。让我创建一个简单的格式化脚本来生成审核消息。先用exec运行一个Python代码片段来格式化。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_9PELzFlSQwMA3JWvwmzY9RSw","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspace && /usr/bin/python3 -c \"\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 读取研究数据\nwith open('memory/research/research_商汤科技_20260414_103343.json', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    data = json.load(f)\n\ncompany_name = data['company_name']\n\n# 开始构建消息\noutput = []\noutput.append(f'【资料审核】{company_name}信息汇总')\noutput.append(f'收集时间: {datetime.now().strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\\\")}')\noutput.append('')\n\ndimension_names = {\n    'technology': '技术维度',\n    'growth': '增长维度', \n    'cost': '成本维度',\n    'competition': '竞争维度',\n    'team': '团队维度'\n}\n\nreliability_emoji = {'A': '🟢', 'B': '🟡', 'C': '🟠', 'D': '🔴'}\n\nfor dim_key, dim_name in dimension_names.items():\n    if dim_key in data['dimensions']:\n        items = data['dimensions'][dim_key].get('info', [])\n        if items:\n            output.append(f'## {dim_name}')\n            output.append('')\n            \n            for i, item in enumerate(items, 1):\n                emoji = reliability_emoji.get(item.get('reliability', 'C'), '⚪')\n                output.append(f'{i}. 【{emoji}{item[\\\"reliability\\\"]}级】{item[\\\"aspect\\\"]}：{item[\\\"info\\\"]}')\n                output.append(f'   来源：{item[\\\"source\\\"]}（{item[\\\"date\\\"]}）')\n                if item.get('url'):\n                    output.append(f'   链接：{item[\\\"url\\\"]}')\n                output.append('')\n\noutput.append('## 总结')\noutput.append(f'- 总信息条数：20')\noutput.append(f'- 收集时间：{data[\\\"collection_date\\\"][:10]}')\noutput.append('')\noutput.append('请审核以上信息，确认无误后回复\\\"批准分析\\\"。')\n\nprint('\\\\n'.join(output))\n\" 2>&1 | head -80"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":530,"output":750,"cacheRead":84032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85312,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776134109795,"responseId":"f3979437-7e1b-4e12-9511-97dec9443b5f"}}
