n                    <div class=\"analyst-name\">分析师：OpenClaw Investment Research</div>\n                    <div class=\"disclaimer\">本报告仅供参考，不构成投资建议</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 执行摘要 -->\n        <div class=\"page summary-page\">\n            <h2><i class=\"fas fa-bullseye\"></i> 执行摘要</h2>\n            <div class=\"executive-summary\">\n                {executive_summary}\n            </div>\n            \n\n[133 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776150354656}}
