{"type":"message","id":"2c28ae35","parentId":"c8a18cfd","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:45:18.911Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户对当前的HTML渲染效果不满意，认为\"丑爆了\"。他提到了一个GitHub仓库：VoltAgent/awesome-design-md，要我去下载里面的DESIGN.md文件，以后每次渲染都参考这个设计文件。\n\n我需要先读取当前的投资分析报告HTML渲染代码，看看它的结构和样式。然后去GitHub下载DESIGN.md文件。既然用户说\"VoltAgent/awesome-design-md - GitHub\"，这很可能是一个GitHub仓库，我可以直接访问 `https://github.com/VoltAgent/awesome-design-md` 来获取文件。\n\n首先，我需要检查当前的HTML模板和样式。然后，使用web_fetch或curl下载DESIGN.md文件，保存到skill目录的references文件夹中。最后，修改html_renderer.py，让它读取DESIGN.md中的设计指导。\n\n让我先看看当前的HTML模板和CSS样式。接着下载DESIGN.md文件。然后分析如何改进设计。可能需要创建一个新的HTML模板，或者修改现有的CSS。用户要求\"每次渲染的时候参考这个DESIGN.md文件进行设计\"，这意味着我需要解析DESIGN.md中的设计规范，或者至少将其作为设计参考。\n\n开始执行。首先，检查当前的report_template.html和style.css。然后下载DESIGN.md。最后，修改渲染器以使用新设计。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_dqa4w3TzvHKvvU8OSoe5wqqw","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/assets/report_template.html","offset":1,"limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":4925,"output":622,"cacheRead":45696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51243,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776156301084,"responseId":"2028a437-2f2c-48da-8dd0-5789294b8fb6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f02b0ba5","parentId":"2c28ae35","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:45:18.915Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_dqa4w3TzvHKvvU8OSoe5wqqw","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>{company_name} - AI投资分析报告</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Source+Code+Pro:wght@400;500&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 报告容器 -->\n    <div class=\"report-container\">\n        <!-- 封面页 -->\n        <div class=\"page cover-page\">\n            <div class=\"cover-content\">\n                <div class=\"cover-badge\">AI投资分析报告</div>\n                <h1 class=\"company-name\">{company_name}</h1>\n                <div class=\"cover-subtitle\">深度五维分析报告</div>\n                \n                <div class=\"cover-metrics\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-item\">\n                        <div class=\"metric-value\">{investment_rating}</div>\n                        <div class=\"metric-label\">投资评级</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-item\">\n                        <div class=\"metric-value\">{target_valuation}</div>\n                        <div class=\"metric-label\">目标估值</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-item\">\n                        <div class=\"metric-value\">{industry_rank}</div>\n                        <div class=\"metric-label\">行业排名</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"cover-footer\">\n                    <div class=\"report-date\">报告日期：{report_date}</div>\n                    <div class=\"analyst-name\">分析师：OpenClaw Investment Research</div>\n                    <div class=\"disclaimer\">本报告仅供参考，不构成投资建议</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 执行摘要 -->\n        <div class=\"page summary-page\">\n            <h2><i class=\"fas fa-bullseye\"></i> 执行摘要</h2>\n            <div class=\"executive-summary\">\n                {executive_summary}\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"key-metrics-grid\">\n                <div class=\"metric-card {tech_score_class}\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-title\">技术评分</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-value\">{tech_score}/10</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-desc\">{tech_highlight}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"metric-card {growth_score_class}\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-title\">增长评分</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-value\">{growth_score}/10</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-desc\">{growth_highlight}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"metric-card {cost_score_class}\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-title\">成本评分</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-value\">{cost_score}/10</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-desc\">{cost_assessment}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"metric-card {competition_score_class}\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-title\">竞争评分</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-value\">{competition_score}/10</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-desc\">{competitive_advantage}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"metric-card {team_score_class}\">\n                    <div class=\"metric-title\">团队评分</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-value\">{team_score}/10</div>\n                    <div class=\"metric-desc\">{team_highlight}</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 五维分析详情 -->\n        <div class=\"page analysis-page\">\n            <h2><i class=\"fas fa-chart-network\"></i> 五维深度分析</h2>\n            \n            <!-- 技术维度 -->\n            <div class=\"dimension-section\" id=\"technology\">\n                <h3><span class=\"dimension-icon\">🔬</span> 技术维度</h3>\n                <div class=\"dimension-content\">\n                    {technology_content}\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"reliability-badge reliability-{tech_reliability}\">可靠性：{tech_reliability_label}</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <!-- 增长维度 -->\n            <div class=\"dimension-section\" id=\"growth\">\n                <h3><span class=\"dimension-icon\">📈</span> 增长维度</h3>\n                <div class=\"dimension-content\">\n                    {growth_content}\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"reliability-badge reliability-{growth_reliability}\">可靠性：{growth_reliability_label}</div>\n            </div>\n\n[83 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776156318914}}
