{"type":"message","id":"70f2ae68","parentId":"502dd6d8","timestamp":"2026-04-14T08:53:27.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在，创建新的CSS文件。我将基于DESIGN.md中的规范编写。首先，定义CSS变量，然后定义通用样式，最后是组件样式。让我创建新的style.css。使用write工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_YyEIZ0V6lse28E7mH97MAqMa","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/investment-xhs/assets/style.css","content":"/* style.css - 基于DESIGN.md的现代投资分析报告样式 */\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   1. CSS变量 - 设计令牌\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n:root {\n  /* 主色调 */\n  --primary-900: #0f172a;\n  --primary-800: #1e293b;\n  --primary-700: #334155;\n  --primary-600: #475569;\n  \n  /* 强调色 */\n  --accent-600: #2563eb;\n  --accent-500: #3b82f6;\n  --accent-400: #60a5fa;\n  \n  /* 语义色 */\n  --success-600: #059669;\n  --success-100: #d1fae5;\n  --warning-600: #d97706;\n  --warning-100: #fef3c7;\n  --danger-600: #dc2626;\n  --danger-100: #fee2e2;\n  \n  /* 中性色 */\n  --gray-900: #111827;\n  --gray-800: #1f2937;\n  --gray-700: #374151;\n  --gray-600: #4b5563;\n  --gray-400: #9ca3af;\n  --gray-300: #d1d5db;\n  --gray-200: #e5e7eb;\n  --gray-100: #f3f4f6;\n  --gray-50: #f9fafb;\n  --white: #ffffff;\n  \n  /* 渐变 */\n  --gradient-primary: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-900) 0%, var(--primary-800) 100%);\n  --gradient-accent: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-600) 0%, var(--accent-500) 100%);\n  \n  /* 阴影 */\n  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n  --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n  --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n  --shadow-xl: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n  --shadow-accent: 0 4px 12px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);\n  \n  /* 间距系统 (8px基准) */\n  --space-1: 4px;\n  --space-2: 8px;\n  --space-3: 12px;\n  --space-4: 16px;\n  --space-6: 24px;\n  --space-8: 32px;\n  --space-12: 48px;\n  --space-16: 64px;\n  --space-24: 96px;\n  \n  /* 边框半径 */\n  --radius-sm: 4px;\n  --radius-md: 8px;\n  --radius-lg: 12px;\n  --radius-xl: 16px;\n  --radius-full: 9999px;\n  \n  /* 字体大小 */\n  --text-xs: 12px;\n  --text-sm: 14px;\n  --text-base: 16px;\n  --text-lg: 18px;\n  --text-xl: 20px;\n  --text-2xl: 24px;\n  --text-3xl: 30px;\n  --text-4xl: 36px;\n  --text-5xl: 48px;\n  --text-6xl: 60px;\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   2. 基础样式重置\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n* {\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\nhtml {\n  font-size: 16px;\n  scroll-behavior: smooth;\n}\n\nbody {\n  font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  color: var(--gray-900);\n  background-color: var(--gray-50);\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   3. 排版系统\n   ========================================================================== */\n\nh1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n  font-weight: 700;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n  color: var(--primary-900);\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);\n  letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n}\n\nh1 {\n  font-size: var(--text-5xl);\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);\n}\n\nh2 {\n  font-size: var(--text-3xl);\n  padding-bottom: var(--space-4);\n  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-500);\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);\n}\n\nh3 {\n  font-size: var(--text-2xl);\n  margin-top: var(--space-12);\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);\n  color: var(--primary-700);\n}\n\nh4 {\n  font-size: var(--text-xl);\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);\n  color: var(--primary-600);\n}\n\np {\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);\n  line-height: 1.7;\n}\n\na {\n  color: var(--accent-600);\n  text-decoration: none;\n  transition: color 0.2s;\n}\n\na:hover {\n  color: var(--accent-500);\n  text-decoration: underline;\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   4. 报告容器布局\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n.report-container {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  background: var(--white);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);\n  overflow: hidden;\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n}\n\n.page {\n  padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-24);\n  min-height: 100vh;\n}\n\n.page:last-child {\n  border-bottom: none;\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   5. 封面页样式\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n.cover-page {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  background: var(--gradient-primary);\n  color: var(--white);\n  text-align: center;\n  position: relative;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.cover-page::before {\n  content: '';\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 0;\n  left: 0;\n  right: 0;\n  bottom: 0;\n  background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);\n}\n\n.cover-content {\n  max-width: 800px;\n  position: relative;\n  z-index: 1;\n}\n\n.cover-badge {\n  display: inline-block;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);\n  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n  padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-6);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-full);\n  font-size: var(--text-sm);\n  font-weight: 500;\n  letter-spacing: 1px;\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-12);\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n}\n\n.company-name {\n  font-size: var(--text-6xl);\n  font-weight: 800;\n  margin: var(--space-6) 0;\n  line-height: 1.1;\n  letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n}\n\n.cover-subtitle {\n  font-size: var(--text-2xl);\n  opacity: 0.9;\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-16);\n  font-weight: 300;\n  letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n}\n\n.cover-metrics {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  gap: var(--space-16);\n  margin: var(--space-16) 0;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n\n.metric-item {\n  text-align: center;\n  min-width: 140px;\n}\n\n.metric-value {\n  font-size: var(--text-4xl);\n  font-weight: 700;\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-2);\n}\n\n.metric-label {\n  font-size: var(--text-sm);\n  opacity: 0.8;\n  letter-spacing: 1px;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n}\n\n.cover-footer {\n  margin-top: var(--space-24);\n  font-size: var(--text-sm);\n  opacity: 0.7;\n  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n  padding-top: var(--space-6);\n}\n\n.report-date, .analyst-name {\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-2);\n}\n\n.disclaimer {\n  margin-top: var(--space-4);\n  font-size: var(--text-xs);\n  opacity: 0.6;\n  max-width: 600px;\n  margin-left: auto;\n  margin-right: auto;\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   6. 执行摘要区域\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n.summary-page {\n  background: var(--gray-50);\n}\n\n.executive-summary {\n  font-size: var(--text-lg);\n  line-height: 1.8;\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-12);\n  padding: var(--space-8);\n  background: var(--white);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n  border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-500);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);\n}\n\n.key-metrics-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n  gap: var(--space-6);\n  margin-top: var(--space-12);\n}\n\n.metric-card {\n  padding: var(--space-8);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n  text-align: center;\n  transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  background: var(--white);\n  border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);\n}\n\n.metric-card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-4px);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);\n}\n\n.metric-card.positive {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--success-100) 0%, rgba(209, 250, 229, 0.7) 100%);\n  border-color: rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.2);\n}\n\n.metric-card.neutral {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--warning-100) 0%, rgba(254, 243, 199, 0.7) 100%);\n  border-color: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.2);\n}\n\n.metric-card.negative {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--danger-100) 0%, rgba(254, 226, 226, 0.7) 100%);\n  border-color: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.2);\n}\n\n.metric-title {\n  font-size: var(--text-sm);\n  color: var(--gray-600);\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);\n  font-weight: 500;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n}\n\n.metric-value {\n  font-size: var(--text-3xl);\n  font-weight: 700;\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-2);\n  color: var(--primary-900);\n}\n\n.metric-desc {\n  font-size: var(--text-sm);\n  color: var(--gray-600);\n  line-height: 1.4;\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   7. 五维分析区域\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n.analysis-page {\n  background: var(--white);\n}\n\n.dimension-section {\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-16);\n  padding: var(--space-8);\n  background: var(--gray-50);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n  border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-500);\n  transition: all 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.dimension-section:hover {\n  transform: translateX(4px);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);\n}\n\n.dimension-section h3 {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: var(--space-3);\n  margin-top: 0;\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);\n  color: var(--primary-800);\n}\n\n.dimension-icon {\n  font-size: var(--text-2xl);\n}\n\n.dimension-content {\n  font-size: var(--text-base);\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  color: var(--gray-700);\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);\n}\n\n.dimension-content p {\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);\n}\n\n.reliability-badge {\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-4);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-full);\n  font-size: var(--text-xs);\n  font-weight: 600;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n}\n\n.reliability-a {\n  background: var(--success-100);\n  color: var(--success-600);\n  border: 1px solid var(--success-600);\n}\n\n.reliability-b {\n  background: var(--warning-100);\n  color: var(--warning-600);\n  border: 1px solid var(--warning-600);\n}\n\n.reliability-c {\n  background: var(--danger-100);\n  color: var(--danger-600);\n  border: 1px solid var(--danger-600);\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   8. 风险评估区域\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n.risk-page {\n  background: var(--gray-50);\n}\n\n.risk-list {\n  list-style: none;\n  margin: var(--space-8) 0;\n}\n\n.risk-list li {\n  padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6);\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);\n  background: var(--white);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-md);\n  border-left: 3px solid var(--warning-600);\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: flex-start;\n  gap: var(--space-3);\n}\n\n.risk-list li::before {\n  content: '⚠️';\n  font-size: var(--text-lg);\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   9. 投资建议区域\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n.recommendation-page {\n  background: var(--white);\n}\n\n.rating-display {\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-8);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-full);\n  font-size: var(--text-2xl);\n  font-weight: 700;\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);\n}\n\n.rating-buy {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--success-100) 0%, rgba(209, 250, 229, 0.9) 100%);\n  color: var(--success-600);\n  border: 2px solid var(--success-600);\n}\n\n.rating-hold {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--warning-100) 0%, rgba(254, 243, 199, 0.9) 100%);\n  color: var(--warning-600);\n  border: 2px solid var(--warning-600);\n}\n\n.rating-sell {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--danger-100) 0%, rgba(254, 226, 226, 0.9) 100%);\n  color: var(--danger-600);\n  border: 2px solid var(--danger-600);\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   10. 可靠性评估表格\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n.reliability-table {\n  width: 100%;\n  border-collapse: collapse;\n  margin: var(--space-8) 0;\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.reliability-table th {\n  background: var(--primary-800);\n  color: var(--white);\n  font-weight: 600;\n  text-align: left;\n  padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6);\n  font-size: var(--text-sm);\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n}\n\n.reliability-table td {\n  padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6);\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);\n  font-size: var(--text-sm);\n}\n\n.reliability-table tr:last-child td {\n  border-bottom: none;\n}\n\n.reliability-table tr:hover {\n  background: var(--gray-50);\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   11. 页脚样式\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n.footer-page {\n  background: var(--primary-900);\n  color: var(--gray-300);\n  text-align: center;\n  padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-24);\n}\n\n.footer-logo {\n  font-size: var(--text-2xl);\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: var(--white);\n  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);\n}\n\n.footer-contact {\n  font-size: var(--text-sm);\n  opacity: 0.7;\n  margin-top: var(--space-8);\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   12. 响应式设计\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n@media (max-width: 1024px) {\n  .page {\n    padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-16);\n  }\n  \n  .company-name {\n    font-size: var(--text-5xl);\n  }\n  \n  .cover-metrics {\n    gap: var(--space-8);\n  }\n  \n  .key-metrics-grid {\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n  }\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .page {\n    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-6);\n  }\n  \n  .company-name {\n    font-size: var(--text-4xl);\n  }\n  \n  .cover-subtitle {\n    font-size: var(--text-xl);\n  }\n  \n  .cover-metrics {\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: var(--space-8);\n  }\n  \n  .key-metrics-grid {\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n  }\n  \n  .metric-value {\n    font-size: var(--text-2xl);\n  }\n  \n  h1 {\n    font-size: var(--text-4xl);\n  }\n  \n  h2 {\n    font-size: var(--text-2xl);\n  }\n  \n  h3 {\n    font-size: var(--text-xl);\n  }\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\n  .page {\n    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-4);\n  }\n  \n  .company-name {\n    font-size: var(--text-3xl);\n  }\n  \n  .cover-badge {\n    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-4);\n    font-size: var(--text-xs);\n  }\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   13. 工具类\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n.text-center { text-align: center; }\n.text-right { text-align: right; }\n.text-left { text-align: left; }\n\n.mt-1 { margin-top: var(--space-1); }\n.mt-2 { margin-top: var(--space-2); }\n.mt-4 { margin-top: var(--space-4); }\n.mt-6 { margin-top: var(--space-6); }\n.mt-8 { margin-top: var(--space-8); }\n.mt-12 { margin-top: var(--space-12); }\n\n.mb-1 { margin-bottom: var(--space-1); }\n.mb-2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }\n.mb-4 { margin-bottom: var(--space-4); }\n.mb-6 { margin-bottom: var(--space-6); }\n.mb-8 { margin-bottom: var(--space-8); }\n.mb-12 { margin-bottom: var(--space-12); }\n\n.p-4 { padding: var(--space-4); }\n.p-6 { padding: var(--space-6); }\n.p-8 { padding: var(--space-8); }\n\n.bg-white { background: var(--white); }\n.bg-gray-50 { background: var(--gray-50); }\n.bg-gray-100 { background: var(--gray-100); }\n\n.rounded-lg { border-radius: var(--radius-lg); }\n.rounded-md { border-radius: var(--radius-md); }\n\n.shadow-md { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }\n.shadow-lg { box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   14. 动画效果\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n@keyframes fadeIn {\n  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }\n  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n}\n\n@keyframes slideIn {\n  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-20px); }\n  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }\n}\n\n.fade-in {\n  animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;\n}\n\n.slide-in {\n  animation: slideIn 0.4s ease-out;\n}\n\n.dimension-section {\n  animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out;\n}\n\n.metric-card {\n  animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-out;\n}\n\n/* ==========================================================================\n   15. 打印样式\n   ========================================================================== */\n\n@media print {\n  .report-container {\n    box-shadow: none;\n    max-width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .page {\n    padding: 20px;\n    min-height: auto;\n    page-break-inside: avoid;\n  }\n  \n  .cover-page {\n    background: #0f172a !important;\n    -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;\n    print-color-adjust: exact;\n  }\n  \n  .metric-card:hover {\n    transform: none;\n  }\n  \n  .footer-page {\n    display: none;\n  }\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":251,"output":5069,"cacheRead":88640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93960,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776156642517,"responseId":"0cbf8257-1ed2-4892-a2c9-fa8d0313ea20"}}
