adge.reliability-a` - A级可靠性徽章\n- `.dimension-section` - 五维分析区块\n- `.risk-list` - 风险提示列表\n\n### **5. 交互功能**\n- 悬浮效果: `.metric-card:hover`\n- 动画过渡: `transition: all 0.3s ease`\n- 响应式断点: `@media (max-width: ...)`\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 **技术实现细节**\n\n### **CSS变量应用**\n```css\n/* 在style.css中定义 */\n:root {\n  --primary-900: #0f172a;\n  --accent-600: #2563eb;\n  --space-8: 32px;\n  --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n}\n```\n\n### **组件样式示例**\n```css\n.metric-card {\n  padding: var(--space-8);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n  background: var(--white);\n  border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);\n  transition: all 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.metric-card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-4px);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);\n}\n```\n\n### **响应式设计**\n```css\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .key-metrics-grid {\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n  }\n  .cover-metrics {\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 **HTML渲染流程总结**\n\n```\n原始分析报告 (.md)\n    ↓\nhtml_renderer.py 解析\n    ↓  \n填充HTML模板变量\n    ↓\n应用DESIGN.md设计系统\n    ↓  \n生成专业HTML报告\n    ↓\nPlaywright截图 → PNG图片\n    ↓\nMEDIA标记 → 自动发送\n```\n\n**完整的HTML源码已发送完毕！**"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":472,"output":1025,"cacheRead":96512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98009,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776157378902,"responseId":"343668ff-4350-4840-b72b-e9a2e6392cc2"}}
